msgstr ""
"연결된 서버를 삭제하면 로컬 Mattermost 서버와 원격 Mattermost 서버 간의 신뢰 관계가 "
"끊어집니다."

#: ../../source/onboard/connected-workspaces.rst:187
msgid ""
"Under **Connected Workspaces**, identify the connected workspace you want"
